import React from 'react'
import { Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Start from './pages/Start'
import { ChakraProvider } from "@chakra-ui/react"
import './App.scss'


function App() {

    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Switch>
                <Route path='/' component={Start}/>
            </Switch>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}

export default App
